**Valet Parking:**

- As a user, I want to be able to select the valet parking option from the drop-down menu.
- As a user, I want to be I want to be able to select Valet Parking as my parking option and be charged $12 when I park for five hours or less.
- As a user, I want to be able to select Valet Parking as my parking option and be charged $18 when I park between 5 and 24 hours.
- As a user, I want to be able to select Valet Parking as my parking option and be charged $18 for every 24 hours I leave my car parked here.

**Short-Term Hourly Parking:**

- As a user, I want to be able to select the short-term parking and be charged $2 for the first hour of parking.
- As a user, I want to be able to select the short-term parking and be charged $1 for each additional half hour of parking.
- As a user, I want to be able to select the short-term parking and be charged a maximum of $24 for parking for 24 hours.
- As a user, I want to be able to use the short-term hourly parking option without any issues.
- As a user, I want to be able to exit the parking lot without any issues after paying the hourly parking fee.

**Long-Term Garage Parking:**

- As a user, I want to be able to use the long-term garage parking option without any issues.
- As a user, I want to be able to select the long-term garage parking and be charged $2 per hour for parking.
- As a user, I want to be able to select the long-term garage parking and be charged a maximum of $12 per day for parking.
- As a user, I want to be able to select the long-term garage parking and be charged $72 per week for parking, with the seventh day being free.
- As a user, I want to be able to exit the parking lot without any issues after paying the long-term garage parking fee.

