**Invalid Options:**

- As a user, I want to be informed when I select an invalid date, such as February 30th, 2023.
- As a user, I want to be informed when I select a departure time that is earlier than the arrival time.
- As a user, I want to be informed when I stay for 0 minutes, and the parking lot should not charge me anything.
